### get all stations
GET http://localhost:8082/station?page=0&size=10&sort=creationDate,desc
Content-Type: application/json

### get station by id
GET http://localhost:8082/station/station-1
Content-Type: application/json

### get station with a port
GET http://localhost:8082/station/station-1/port/1

### update a port status
PUT http://localhost:8082/station/station-123/port/port-1
Content-Type: application/json

